# cohort-component-spec-writer Skill

> Source: `~/Development/cohort/.claude/skills/cohort-component-spec-writer/SKILL.md`

## Triggers
"write a spec for", "document this component", "design handoff", "create component docs", "spec out the Button", or pre-implementation design document.

## Output target
`~/Development/cohort/docs/components/<name>.md` 영역 single markdown file.

## Locked template
1. **Component name + variant**
2. **Props table** (type / default / required / description)
3. **States** (default / hover / focus / active / disabled / loading)
4. **Accessibility note** (ARIA / keyboard / screen reader / contrast)
5. **Mascot integration** (Aurora / Vesper voice usage if applicable)
6. **Copy guidelines** (Korean primary + English fallback + Option B compliance)
7. **Mobile-first responsive** (mobile 360px / md 768px / lg 1024px)
8. **Token sourcing** (vault 42 §2.1 + tailwind.config 정합)
